@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zalana(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.21)))
    v1 = (0.04 - wp.cos((v1 + 0.12 + tmp + 0.47)))
    tmp = 0.42
    v2 = v1
    v1 = wp.cos((0.87 / wp.cos(v2 + 0.78)))
    v2 = ((0.93 * wp.abs(v1 + 0.65)) / wp.sin((tmp + 0.49 - v1 + 0.84)))
    v2 = 0.20
    data[tid] = v0
